data.description: Florida living at its finest, a boat enthusiast's dream and 150ft of bulkhead. HIGH AND DRY, NO FLOODING! This stunning 3 bedroom (with additional flex room for a 4th sleeping area or office) 2.5 bath canal home is ready to enjoy all that beautiful Flagler Beach has to offer. Located on a deep salt water canal, easy access to the Intracoastal Waterway with a newer boat dock and boat lift for easy loading and unloading and a 3 car garage! This stunning custom home has it all! Granite counters, stainless appliances, tile floors throughout, extra large walk in shower in the newly renovated master bedroom and bath, stunning back lanai with fire pit and beautiful water views with dolphins and manatees swimming by! Enjoy grilling under the extra large covered back patio or your private dock, or you can relax and watch the sun go down from the covered front porch. Located at the end of a cut-de-sac among a charming quiet neighborhood. Golf cart to restaurants or boutiques at downtown Flagler. There is plenty of room to store all your water toys with a 3 car garage. Lush tropical landscape with irrigation.  Smart technology throughout. 25 minutes S of St. Augustine and 25 minutes N. of Daytona. 5 minutes from I95.
